```plantuml
@startuml McOrts_taller-iot-sensor_radiactividad

actor User

participant "ESP8266" as ESP
participant "Geiger Counter Module" as GCM
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT
participant "Node-RED" as NR
participant "GMC.MAP" as GMC

User -> ESP: Configure Wi-Fi & MQTT settings
ESP -> GCM: Start pulse detection
GCM -> ESP: Pulse detected
ESP -> ESP: Calculate CPM
ESP -> MQTT: Publish CPM data
MQTT -> NR: Forward CPM data
NR -> GMC: Send data for visualization

User -> MQTT: Send LED control command
MQTT -> ESP: Receive LED control command
ESP -> ESP: Toggle LED state

@enduml
```